channel.title: I need a bit of help
channel.description:
i am new to this and i wnt to know how to make my own server!... i have downloaded a source(project16_v.3), i have made a no-ip... how do i upload my source to my no-ip?... or what the hell do i do!.. please help me.
(note: ^^ there is no leet)
i will be very greatful if you could help me.

item.title: I need a bit of help
item.dc:creator: @craids craids
item.description:
@craids wrote:

once you made the no-ip download it, click the little check box next to your ip, now go onto moparscape.go into your servers file and click run server.Now your server is up, all you have to do is go in with the ip “127.0.0.1” (no quotes) and others will go with the ip you made.
